  &= c + k\nu\log\big|(\nu-p-1)\vPsi\big| - \sum_{a=1}^k (n_a + \nu)\log\big|(\nu-p-1)\vPsi + \vS_a\big|\\
  &= c' + k\nu\log\big|\vPsi\big| - \sum_{a=1}^k (n_a + \nu)\log\big|\vPsi + (\nu-p-1)^{-1}\vS_a\big|.
\end{align*}
Since $(\nu-p-1)^{-1}\vS_a$ is only dependent on data we can set $(\nu-p-1)^{-1}\vS_a
:= \S_a$. Hence, without loss of generality we consider
\begin{align}
  2\ell(\vPsi)
  = c + k\nu\log\big|\vPsi\big| - \sum_{a=1}^k (n_a + \nu)\log\big|\vPsi + \vS_a\big|,
  \label{eq:loglik2}
\end{align}
throughout this chapter.

